SUMMARY:Let’s Get Mossy! Spring Kokedama Workshop at Gallery Grow
DESCRIPTION:Create your own kokedama at our BYOB happy hour workshop. Includes saucer; upgrades 20% off. $25/person.Unwind with us at this intimate\, BYOB happy hour workshop and explore the art of kokedama—Japanese “moss ball” planting. You’ll create your own kokedama while learning its history and simple care tips for home. The workshop includes select embellishments and a bamboo disc or saucer\, with upgraded containers available at 20% off during the event. $25 per person.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/lets-get-mossy-spring-kokedama-workshop-at-gallery-grow/
LOCATION:Gallery Grow Plant Bar\, 320 N Queen St.\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes and Workshops
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/GG-Kokedama-HH.jpeg
ORGANIZER;CN="Gallery Grow Plant Bar":MAILTO:contact@gallerygrow.com
END:VEVENT
