SUMMARY:Spring Fashion Show at the Stevens School Ballroom
DESCRIPTION:Step into the season in style. Lancaster’s Spring Fashion Show brings local boutiques to the runway for an evening of elevated looks\, fresh inspiration\, and timeless silhouettes designed to carry you through the months ahead. Set inside the historic Stevens School Ballroom\, this immersive event highlights women’s\, men’s\, and children’s fashion from some of the area’s most beloved retailers. Expect thoughtfully styled collections\, a lively runway presentation\, and the opportunity to shop select pieces featured in the show. The evening begins with a complimentary champagne welcome\, light bites\, curated goodie bags\, and a cash bar\, setting the tone for a stylish night centered on local fashion. Shop\, sip\, and be inspired as spring style takes the spotlight. A portion of the evening’s proceeds will be donated to the Ann B. Barshinger Cancer Institute in support of their important work within our community. Featured Boutiques: Fourteenth Boutique (Women’s) Zanzibar (Women’s) J.Hilburn (Men’s) Ellicott & Co. (Men’s) Bellaboo (Children’s) Full list coming soon!
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/spring-fashion-show-at-the-stevens-school-ballroom/
LOCATION:The Stevens School Ballroom\, 355 W Chestnut St\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Special Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/Spring-Fashion-Show-Visit-Lancaster-City-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Ecklin Events":MAILTO:info@ecklinevents.com
END:VEVENT
