SUMMARY:Saturday Night Improv: TourCo Home Game
DESCRIPTION:Our touring company shows off their talents at the home base; it’s a smorgasbord of improv shenanigans! \n\n\n\nHere at Lancaster Improv Players University our top notch sports team is always at away games…until now! Come see our Touring Company play a home game at our theater; peanuts and cracker jacks optional. \n\n\n\n$15 at the doorBYOB \n\n\n\nLANCASTER IMPROV PLAYERS is an intimate black box venue located in the heart of Lancaster City. With a capacity of approximately 30 guests\, that means this Lancaster comedy club is entirely front row. Not a nosebleed in sight! After all\, BYOB is just a drink special you never get tired of.
