SUMMARY:Easter Brunch at Annie Bailey's
DESCRIPTION:We will be open for Easter brunch on April 5th at 11am. We’ll have a brunch buffet with favorites such as a smoked salmon platter or biscuits & gravy\, as well as a chef attended omelet station. The brunch buffet is $30 per person. Grab your friends and family and come celebrate with us!
