SUMMARY:Adult Beginner Salsa
DESCRIPTION:It’s never too late to break in those dancing shoes! Learn the basic steps of salsa dancing in this engaging\, high-energy class designed for adult beginners. ¡Vámonos! What to wear: • Comfortable\, breathable clothing that allows for movement (e.g. leggings\, athletic wear\, t-shirts) • Jazz shoes\, dance shoes\, or clean sneakers • Hair pulled back if long • Water bottle encouraged for hydration
