SUMMARY:Shawan Rice & The Quiet Riders
DESCRIPTION:Treat yourself to a night under the stars featuring the best of local music! Soulful\, rootsy\, unique: these innovative artists and Central PA natives deliver inventive tunes that will have you grooving in your seat. Originally from the midstate\, Shawan Rice toured the U.S. before relocating to New Orleans\, where her captivating voice has made her a staple in the city’s vibrant music scene. Lancaster-based band The Quiet Riders share a deep love for American music\, earning them a Central PA Music Award for “Best Funk Band” in 2024. Taking place in the stunning glass pyramid-topped Atrium of the Ware Center\, the “Lancaster Loves” series features the best in local music across a variety of genres in a lively cabaret setting.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/shawan-rice-the-quiet-riders/
LOCATION:The Ware Center – Millersville University\, 42 N. Prince Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Music and Dance
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/2026.04.10-Shawan-Rice-The-Quiet-Riders.jpg
END:VEVENT
